Weekly Weather Plays gives you the unique ability to protect your business against weather-related exposure. 

Who needs Weekly Weather Plays?


Crude oil, coal and gas distributors - Weekly Weather Plays allows you to protect your revenues by using weather trading to hedge against weather-related fuel supply demand shortages; 
Utilities - Weather trading allows you to hedge against weather-related energy supply demand decreases; 
Financial/Insurance Institutions - Weather risk trading allows you to reduce your exposure to weather-related claims and investments - and is also a unique offering in any portfolio. 

